title: U2 - Live - 1987-10-20 - Iowa City, Iowa USA - Video
description:
U2
1987-10-20
Carver Hawkeye Arena
Iowa City

audience shot from Adam's side. Not the best recording, it's shot from the audience using a hand-held recorder. Honestly, it isn't "that bad", very watchable. I've seen a lot worse.

The audio is from an unknown audio recording, possibly soundboard. This is a good thing, as it's much better than the audio from the actual recording.
